Title: Valedictorian Speech | Ryan Trahan, Rice High School Class of 2017
Description:
Ryan Trahan's (windy) valedictorian speech at the 2017 Rice High School Graduation in Altair, Texas. 

I hope you all enjoy my valedictory address! I wanted to include personal anecdotes and also messages that people could apply to their own lives. 

High school has been an amazing journey and I honestly can't believe how far we have all come as individuals on our personal journeys. I look forward to the future with excitement and a full heart.

Thank you for all of your everlasting support.
